Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}我這邊又沒有什麼你見不得人的畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}模...模型的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}之前給你看過的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}德軍第四代戰車H型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}啊？那台戰車不是頗受好評嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}其他的模型玩家也讚不絕口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}大家都說你開竅了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}不是的...
